          "description": "I have no complaints about this urgent care center. I was seen within 15 minutes. It's very clean, quiet and staffed by friendly people. I was seen by Dr.Feldman. He was warm and caring. Took whatever time was necessary to assess my needs and suggested the course of treatment. I felt confident in his advice, and what he prescribed. Feeling better already! One added plus is that my primary care doctor is in the same building, and she's wonderful.",
