          "description": "This is the best Urgent Care I have visited. The young lady at the front desk was very attentive and the Assistant (Adrienne) was courteous/caring. The Dr's were cordial and listened to my medical problem with compassion. The wait time was very quick and the facility was clean and comfortable.\n\nI would recommend this Urgent Care to anyone who needs compassionate attention to their medical needs.",
