          "description": "I had an excellent experience at Mount Sinai Urgent Care on the Upper West Side. The entire team is highly professional, organized, and efficient from start to finish. The reception staff are outstanding both in person and over the phone - responsive, clear, and able to handle any request quickly and smoothly.\n\nI especially appreciated their alertness and transparency when it came to insurance, which made the process stress-free. The doctors and medical assistants are clearly very skilled: they do exactly what needs to be done, no more and no less, with care and precision.\n\nTruly great care, professionalism, and efficiency across the board. Highly recommended.",
