          "description": "On my latest visit to Mt. Sinai urgent care on Columbus was on 10|2. I saw Dr. Cicatelli who was just fantastic.  He treated me with kindness and clarity about my. skin problem, prescribed the right medicine and gave me clear paperwork about the entire situation including where to go for follow-up if needed. Every time I have had to go to the urgent care there, which is near to my house, I have had excellent care from the front desk, the nurses, and the doctors. . I recommend them very highly. And feel lucky to have such a competent urgent care a few blocks from my house.",
